@startuml


title Sequence Diagram: Artwork Persistence Flow& Storage Sync

actor User

participant "PaintableSurfaceRT" as Surface
participant "UI / Save Menu" as UI
participant "SupabaseArtworkRepository" as ArtworkRepo
participant "Supabase.Client (SDK)" as SupabaseSDK
database "Local Disk" as Disk
database "Supabase Storage" as Storage
database "Supabase Database" as DB

== Serialization ==
User -> UI: Click Save Artwork
UI -> Surface: SaveCanvasToPNG(fileName)
Surface -> Surface: Texture2D.ReadPixels(RenderTexture)
Surface -> Surface: tex.EncodeToPNG()
Surface -> Disk: File.WriteAllBytes(path)
Surface -> UI: Return localPath

== Cloud Upload ==
UI -> ArtworkRepo: CreateArtworkWithUploadAsync(artworkData, bytes)
ArtworkRepo -> ArtworkRepo: Generate Thumbnail (GenerateHalfSizePng)
ArtworkRepo -> SupabaseSDK: UploadObjectAsync(original)
SupabaseSDK -> Storage: POST /storage/v1/object/artwork-images
ArtworkRepo -> SupabaseSDK: UploadObjectAsync(thumbnail)
SupabaseSDK -> Storage: POST /storage/v1/object/artwork-images

== Metadata Sync ==
ArtworkRepo -> ArtworkRepo: Set image_url & thumbnail_url
ArtworkRepo -> SupabaseSDK: client.From<ArtworkData>().Insert(artwork)
SupabaseSDK -> DB: INSERT INTO artwork
DB -> SupabaseSDK: OK / Created Model
SupabaseSDK -> ArtworkRepo: Return Model
ArtworkRepo -> UI: Return Success
UI -> User: Display "Saved Selection"

@enduml
